NAME        pentalenolactone synthase;
            penM (gene name);
            pntM (gene name)
CLASS       Oxidoreductases;
            Acting on paired donors, with incorporation or reduction of molecular oxygen;
            With oxidation of a pair of donors resulting in the reduction of O2 to two molecules of water
SYSNAME     pentalenolactone-reduced-ferredoxin:oxygen oxidoreductase (pentalenolactone forming)
